title: Camel Stock, World by Country, 1961-2004
name: Camel Stock, World by Country, 1961-2004
description: This data set illustrates the camel stock, by thousand head, by country from 1961 to 2004.  A value of -1 means that no data was available.  Camel stocks can be further defined as including all camels in the country regardless of place or purpose of their breeding. Camel figures include Bactrian camel (Camelus bactrianus) and Arabian camel (C. dromedarius)" (Earth Trends).
